title: [Western Harbor, Jetty]
description: Tangled knots of seaweed clutter the sandstone blocks of the jetty, their ends glistening in the sunlight and fluttering in the sea breeze.  The thunderous crashing of waves along the eastern facing is punctuated by the spray of seawater that falls in a fine mist from the air.
